                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a href="http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S002210311100254X">Neal, Wood, Labrecque, & Lally (2012) - How do habits guide behavior? Perceived and actual triggers of habits in daily life.
                            <em>Journal of Experimental Social Psychology (48)</em>pp. 492-498</a>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
